CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 6, 1966, pg. 1B reads: "Distinguished Frogs and "Miss Frog Week" Meredith Gay Watson, brighten the scene of the brilliant Frogs formal dance held at the Hilton Hotel Friday, July 29th. Left to right are Judge J. Warren Watson, father of Meredith, Charles Rickmond, charter member of the 56 year old club, to the right of Meredith is charter member Harry G. Washington, and "Bud" Leftridge. (Harris Photo).
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Frogs members, from left: Judge J. Warren Watson, Charles Rickmond, Harry G. Washington, and "Bud" Leftridge, posed with "Miss FROGS Week" Meredith Gay Watson in Hilton Hotel for FROGS week ball
